## Install Visual Studio Code (Requires SUDO)

```shell
ansible-playbook -vvv main.yml -i "localhost" --connection="localhost" --extra-vars "state=present" -t="vscode" -K
```

## Uninstall Visual Studio Code with full cleanup (Requires SUDO)

```shell
ansible-playbook -vvv main.yml -i "localhost" --connection="localhost" --extra-vars "state=absent" -t="vscode" -K
```

This removes the `code` package, the Microsoft apt repository and keyring, and the current user's VS Code extensions, cache, and config under `/home/$USER`.